{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Last Nightmare</i> is a top-down game with a pixelated style, combining pixel art with 3D models. Experience the journey of the protagonist as he tries to return home, facing various challenges and unimaginable creatures. Utilize the mechanics of</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Lantern</u></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/video-lanterna.gif?t=1731361870\" />Use it to explore the depths of darkness and uncover the mysteries it hides.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Items and Inventory</u></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/video-inventario.gif?t=1731361870\" />Collect all the items you find; while some will be useful immediately, others will serve as keys to open doors and chests. Additionally, there are cards that reveal hidden parts of the story, encouraging you to investigate every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Running and Stamina System</u></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/video-correr.gif?t=1731361870\" />Extremely useful for escaping from monsters, but be careful not to exhaust yourself. Balance is crucial for ensuring your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Stealth</u></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/agachar.gif?t=1731361870\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel the sound of your breath and heartbeat. This mode is very useful for hiding from certain monsters, but remember: you are not invisible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragrap